<div class="rw-home-about">
== About Religio Wiki ==
Religio Wiki is a collaborative digital project whose purpose is to
provide traditional, reliable, and verified information about the world's
major religions — among them Hinduism, Buddhism, Judaism, Christianity,
Islam, Confucianism, Taoism, and Shinto — drawing from their primary
sources and adopting their most orthodox perspectives, always with
bibliographic references.
